					<td>
					

						<div class="postbody"><div class="quotetitle"><b>Quote:</b></div><div class="quotecontent">So I guess the flag will flip the sprites on their relative (0,0)? If I'm assuming correctly then i just need to position them relative to their flip location?</div><br /><br />Yes, and the anchor point (top left corner) remains the same. So if you have two sprites at 0,0 and 8,0, flip their H mirror and want the whole metasprite to flip, they must be relocated to 8,0 and 0,0.<br /><br />Edit: dougeff ninja'd and got into better detail.</div>

					
