p; LDA buttons1<br />&nbsp; AND #%00100000<br />&nbsp; BEQ PlayerStartPressed<br /><br />&nbsp; LDA buttons1<br />&nbsp; AND #%00010000<br />&nbsp; BEQ PlayerSelectPressed<br /><br />&nbsp; LDA buttons1<br />&nbsp; AND #%00001000<br />&nbsp; BEQ PlayerUpPressed<br /><br />&nbsp; LDA buttons1<br />&nbsp; AND #%00000100<br />&nbsp; BEQ PlayerDownPressed<br /><br />&nbsp; LDA buttons1<br />&nbsp; AND #%00000010<br />&nbsp; BEQ PlayerLeftPressed<br /><br />&nbsp; LDA buttons1<br />&nbsp; AND #%00000001<br />&nbsp; BEQ PlayerRightPressed<br /><br />&nbsp; RTS&nbsp; &nbsp;<br /></div><br /><br />So, hopefully this is a bit closer to what it should look like.  This actually isn't working at all so I'm trying to work through that now.</div>

