					<td>
					

						<div class="postbody">Some things NEED to happen during v-blank.<br /><br />1.DMA Sprites<br />2.PPU Writes (and palette changes)<br />3.Setting the scroll and 2000/2001<br /><br />These must come before anything else.<br /><br />Saving the A,X,Y registers is optional IF you are doing an &quot;all in the NMI&quot; system.</div>

					
						<div class="postbody"><br />_________________<br /><a href="http://nesdoug.com" class="postlink">nesdoug.com</a> -- blog/tutorial on programming for the NES</div>
